Anglo American Says First-Quarter Refined Platinum Output Increased by 19%

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-04-21T06:01:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-21/anglo-american-says-first-quarter-refined-platinum-output-increased-by-19-.html
Anglo American Plc (AAL) , the diversified
mining company, said first quarter refined platinum production
increased 19 percent to 532,900 ounces.  Anglo commented in a stock exchange statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  